		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It uses unofficial opcodes $B3 and $CB. Plus, there's an $01 at offset $9 of the iNES header.
<br />
<br />Works with Nintendulator (prints unofficial opcodes) and Nestopia (switches to PAL mode). Doesn't work on RockNES due to the unofficial opcodes.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


