		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really like how the controls are different than anything I've played before.  Once I actually started to use the B button to speed up I found that you could actually use it while you were already in the air.  If I'm not mistaken, it appears that you can turn "turbo" speed on and off whist in the air.  Frustrating and difficult to master but a neat physics approach IMO.  Is there any other game out there that does this?

		

		</td>
